:Namespace InitializeTests

‚ćĚ Initialize jarvis resolves the absolute app config path ($APL_SERVICE_APP_CONFIG
‚ćĚ if set, else config/app.config.json next to jarvis.CodeSource), loads it
‚ćĚ with LoadAppConfig, and assigns the global AppState.RootFolder, alongside
‚ćĚ AppState.FrontendRoot (jarvis.CodeSource,'/../frontend', the sibling of
‚ćĚ APLSource that Get's static-asset fallback serves from - not
‚ćĚ canonicalised any more than RootFolder's config path is, since real file
‚ćĚ operations resolve the literal '..' segment at the OS level regardless).
‚ćĚ jarvis is whatever Jarvis passes for a monadic AppInitFn: a stub
‚ćĚ namespace exposing just .CodeSource is enough here, since Initialize
‚ćĚ touches nothing else on it. The $APL_SERVICE_APP_CONFIG override itself
‚ćĚ is not exercised here: a running interpreter cannot set its own
‚ćĚ environment variables, so that path is covered by the e2e smoke test,
‚ćĚ which launches a real subprocess with the variable set.

